version_description: Some users upgrading to the latest versions were not getting push notifications, we've fixed that! Now you should be receiving the latest notifications when your searches get new results and when your favorites drop in price!
We put in counter measures to prevent intrusive ads from interrupting your experience.

- Performance updates for faster searches and load times
- Some small UI tweaks

- Fixed infrequently seen bug persisting your downpayment calculation preferences
- Fixed a bug in sorting of favorites
- Performance improvements
Visual and performance tweaks, miscellaneous bug fixes
Performance enhancements and UI improvements for readability.
- Fixed some bugs that caused crashes for some users
Lots of new updates under the hood, for performance and stability improvements.

- Performance enhancements
- Updated UX for account settings and email management
- Bug Fixes
Bug fixes and performance enhancements. Keep auto update turned on to receive all the latest features!
Critical bug fixes, memory management and other performance enhancements. Keep auto update turned on to get all the latest changes and features!

Support for iPhone X and iOS 11.
Bug fixes and performance improvements under the hood.

Enable auto updates to receive all the latest performance upgrades and bug fixes.

- Fixed some issues from iOS 11 and iPhone X
- Fixed an issue causing crashes on load for certain users
- Improved network performance to reduce battery consumption
- Fixed an issue where you could not remove your saved search and it caused a crash

If you have any issues or feedback, feel free to reach out to us at feedback@autolist.com.
